text: 🎉 Registration for ETHNOSPARK 2025 is now open! Register before January 15th to secure your spot.
🎵 Special guest artist Padma Shri Ustad Rahman Khan will be performing at our Musical Night!
👗 Free traditional costumes will be provided for the fashion walk. Contact the organizing committee for details.
🍽️ Food stalls featuring cuisine from 15 different Indian states will be available throughout the day.
🏆 Exciting prizes await winners in various categories including Best Performance, Best Costume, and Best Art.
